data.description: Must see this charming 3 bedroom/2 bath home in highly sought after SE Boise. Location is so important, and this is convenient to the airport, Barber Park, Greenbelt, golfing, the Boise River, and Lucky Peak. Great shopping and medical facilities are also close. Also an extra bonus for veterans with a 2.3% assumable loan. Updates include roof, kitchen countertops to Corian, main bath & fencing. Plenty of room for entertainment in the living room and family room with an adjoining fireplace (double-sided). Enjoy quiet evenings in the backyard with a covered patio and fire pit. Call for those details and schedule to see this before this is gone.
